	dprr:hasNoteText "Disastrously defeated by Viriathus (Liv. Per. 52; App. Ib. 64; Oros. 5.4.3; cf. Diod. 33.2). He later went into exile when prosecuted for imminuta maiestas (Diod. 33.2). See Lübker no. 4." ;
